{"id":1354,"date":"2024-08-04T21:08:08","date_gmt":"2024-08-04T21:08:08","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/?post_type=wiki&#038;p=1354"},"modified":"2024-08-04T21:08:08","modified_gmt":"2024-08-04T21:08:08","slug":"mission-059","status":"publish","type":"wiki","link":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/mission-059\/","title":{"rendered":"Mission #059: Swords of Justice"},"content":{"rendered":"<table class=\"table left grey\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\" class=\"text-large center\">Mission #059: Swords of Justice<\/th>\n<\/tr>\n<\/thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<th>Start Location<\/th>\n<td>Fallshore City, Mission HQ 2F &#8211; Black Belt<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Unlock Requirements<\/th>\n<td>\n<ul>\n<li>Become Pok\u00e9mon Champion<\/li>\n<li>Complete 20 Missions and receive Type:Null from the Pok\u00e9mon Ranger<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Objectives<\/th>\n<td>Capture the three Swords of Justice<\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Reward<\/th>\n<td>\n        <u>Item<\/u>: <strong>10 Fast Balls<\/strong><br \/>\n        <u>Event<\/u>: <strong>Keldeo Capture Opportunity<\/strong>\n      <\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>In the Fallshore Mission HQ, after completing 20 Missions and receiving Type: Null, a Black Belt will ask a favor of you.<\/p>\n<p>If you travel to Victory Road and then capture the Swords of Justice Virizion, Terrakion and Cobalion, he\u2019ll give you 10 Fast Balls. In addition, you\u2019ll be able to capture Keldeo.<\/p>\n<h2>Starting the Mission<\/h2>\n<p>The Mission HQ is on the west side of Fallshore City just north of the Marketplace.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/01-pokemon-unbound-the-fallshore-city-mission-hq.jpg\" alt=\"The Fallshore City Mission HQ \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Fallshore City Mission HQ<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<div class=\"callout-box\">\n<strong>Note:<\/strong> In order to receive this mission, you need to have become Pok\u00e9mon Champion and already completed 20 other missions. You\u2019ll also need to have picked up the reward for that from the Pok\u00e9mon Ranger near the inside doorway of Mission HQ, which is a Type: Null.\n<\/div>\n<p>Go upstairs and into the apartment &#8211; there\u2019s a Black Belt at the table in front of the kitchen. <\/p>\n<p>He tells you that the Swords of Justice are on Victory Road, and you\u2019ll need to head there to catch them.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/02-pokemon-unbound-the-black-belt-upstairs.jpg\" alt=\"The Black Belt upstairs \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Black Belt upstairs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h2>How to Complete<\/h2>\n<p>Fly to Victory Road and you\u2019ll be in front of the Pok\u00e9mon Center on Route 18. From there, go northwest to the Victory Road entrance.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/03-pokemon-unbound-fly-to-victory-road.jpg\" alt=\"Fly to Victory Road \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Fly to Victory Road<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head inside to the first floor of Victory Road.<\/p>\n<p>Then cross the bridge, go down the stairs and surf east to the ladder up to the second floor.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/04-pokemon-unbound-get-to-the-ladder.jpg\" alt=\"Get to the ladder \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Get to the ladder<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>From the ladder, go north and west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/05-pokemon-unbound-victory-road-2f-cavern.jpg\" alt=\"Victory Road 2F cavern \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Victory Road 2F cavern<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>You\u2019ll be at the cavern exit out into the hedge maze. Go through it.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/06-pokemon-unbound-the-cave-exit.jpg\" alt=\"The cave exit \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The cave exit<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3>Virizion<\/h3>\n<p>The first of the Swords of Justice we encounter on Victory Road is Virizion, and it\u2019s somewhere in the hedge maze.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/07-pokemon-unbound-virizion-is-in-this-maze.jpg\" alt=\"Virizion is in this maze \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Virizion is in this maze<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>It\u2019s in the central grass patch, north of the Kindler and Bug Maniac Double Battle trainers.<\/p>\n<p>Approach it, and it\u2019ll run away.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/08-pokemon-unbound-in-the-central-grass-patch.jpg\" alt=\"In the central grass patch \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>In the central grass patch<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/09-pokemon-unbound-youll-need-to-track-it-down.jpg\" alt=\"You\u2019ll need to track it down \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>You\u2019ll need to track it down<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Each member of the Swords of Justice will need to be found several times in order for them to appear at their catching location, and they don\u2019t stray far, sticking to whatever level they\u2019re found on.<\/p>\n<p>Next, go to the very northeast point of the maze and you\u2019ll find Virizion in the dead end.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/10-pokemon-unbound-northeast-dead-end.jpg\" alt=\"Northeast dead end \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Northeast dead end<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>It will then flee directly west to the northwest corner just outside the maze.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/11-pokemon-unbound-northwest-corner.jpg\" alt=\"Northwest corner \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Northwest corner<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After that, it will run to the entrance to the maze.<\/p>\n<p>When you interact with it this time, it will leave the floor completely and go to the 3F cave.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/12-pokemon-unbound-at-the-maze-entrance.jpg\" alt=\"At the maze entrance \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>At the maze entrance<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go north to the 3F entrance at the other end of the maze and head on inside.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/13-pokemon-unbound-head-inside-3f.jpg\" alt=\"Head inside 3F \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Head inside 3F<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3>Terrakion<\/h3>\n<p>As soon as you enter the cave you\u2019ll see Terrakion directly in front of you in that little dead end. Talk to it, and it will run away to its next location on this floor.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/14-pokemon-unbound-terrakions-1st-spot.jpg\" alt=\"Terrakion\u2019s first spot \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Terrakion\u2019s first spot<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Head west and then north to the central part of the cavern.<\/p>\n<p>When you go through this area, you\u2019ll see Virizion has appeared around the central rock. <strong>Don\u2019t<\/strong> interact with it when it\u2019s here, or it will run back to the hedge maze. When all three Swords of Justice retreat to this rock, they\u2019ll be able to be captured.<\/p>\n<p>For now, go past it to the east section of the cavern.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/15-pokemon-unbound-dont-interact-with-virizion-on-the-way-past.jpg\" alt=\"Don\u2019t interact with Virizion on the way past \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Don\u2019t interact with Virizion on the way past<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Terrakion will be hiding here &#8211; talk to it and it will run off to the southwest.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/16-pokemon-unbound-east-section-of-the-cavern.jpg\" alt=\"East section of the cavern \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>East section of the cavern<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After finding it there, it will then move to the cave exit in the northwest.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/17-pokemon-unbound-southwest-part-of-the-cavern.jpg\" alt=\"Southwest part of the cavern \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Southwest part of the cavern<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you approach Terrakion this time, he\u2019ll go to the central rock with Virizion.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/18-pokemon-unbound-the-cave-exit-to-the-snowy-ascent.jpg\" alt=\"The cave exit to the snowy ascent \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The cave exit to the snowy ascent<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>With two of the three Swords of Justice in place, go back to the snowy ascent cavern exit.<\/p>\n<figure class=\"centerme\">\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/19-pokemon-unbound-2-down-1-to-go.jpg\" alt=\"Two down, one to go \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Two down, one to go<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Go outside into the snow, and you\u2019ll need to track down Cobalion.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/20-pokemon-unbound-head-outside.jpg\" alt=\"Head outside \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Head outside<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3>Cobalion<\/h3>\n<p>Once outside in the cold, go east to where Kyurem\u2019s Cave is.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/21-pokemon-unbound-the-snowy-ascent.jpg\" alt=\"The snowy ascent \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The snowy ascent<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>This is the first location you\u2019ll find Cobalion. Interact with it and it\u2019ll run off to the southwest.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/22-pokemon-unbound-cobalion-at-last.jpg\" alt=\"Cobalion at last \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Cobalion at last<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Then, it will run off to the grassy cliff in the northeast.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/23-pokemon-unbound-southwest-above-the-stairs.jpg\" alt=\"Southwest above the stairs \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Southwest above the stairs<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>After that, it will appear in the central rocky area.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/24-pokemon-unbound-northeast-grassy-cliff.jpg\" alt=\"Northeast grassy cliff \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Northeast grassy cliff<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Interact with the Cobalion one final time here and it will go off to join the others.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/25-pokemon-unbound-central-rocky-area.jpg\" alt=\"Central rocky area \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Central rocky area<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<h3>Catching the Swords<\/h3>\n<p>Once all three are in place, you\u2019re free to catch the Swords of Justice one by one. They\u2019re extremely difficult to catch and it\u2019s probably best done with Dusk Balls or Timer Balls.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/35-pokemon-unbound-ready-to-be-caught.jpg\" alt=\"Ready to be caught \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Ready to be caught<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<table class=\"table grey center\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Virizion<\/strong><br \/>\n        Grass\/Fighting<br \/>\n        (Lv. 50)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/26-pokemon-unbound-virizion.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:300px\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Terrakion<\/strong><br \/>\n        Rock\/Fighting<br \/>\n        (Lv. 50)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/27-pokemon-unbound-terrakion.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:300px\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<tr>\n<td>\n        <strong>Cobalion<\/strong><br \/>\n        Steel\/Fighting<br \/>\n        (Lv. 50)\n      <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/28-pokemon-unbound-cobalion.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:300px\"><\/td>\n<\/tr>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n<p>When you\u2019ve got all three, go to the nearest Pok\u00e9mon Center and put them in your party. Then, return to the Black Belt in Fallshore City.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/29-pokemon-unbound-off-to-route-17.jpg\" alt=\"Off to Route 17 \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Off to Route 17<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Show the three Swords of Justice to him, and he\u2019ll tell you to meet him somewhere on Route 17.<\/p>\n<p>Fly to Seaport City and head west.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/30-pokemon-unbound-down-the-bottom-of-the-central-island.jpg\" alt=\"Down the bottom of the central island \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Down the bottom of the central island<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>Surf west until you\u2019re down the bottom of the middle island, on a secluded beach.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/31-pokemon-unbound-the-swords-of-justice-open-the-way.jpg\" alt=\"The Swords of Justice open the way \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>The Swords of Justice open the way<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>When you talk to the Black Belt, the Swords of Justice combine their power to open a cave in the cliff wall.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/32-pokemon-unbound-fast-balls-to-catch-a-fast-pokemon.jpg\" alt=\"Fast Balls to catch a fast Pok\u00e9mon \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Fast Balls to catch a fast Pok\u00e9mon<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<p>The Black Belt will end the mission and reward you with <strong>10 Fast Balls<\/strong>, telling you they\u2019ll help with catching the Pok\u00e9mon inside.<\/p>\n<p>You\u2019ll get an opportunity to catch the other Sword of Justice, Keldeo.<\/p>\n<figure>\n  <img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/33-pokemon-unbound-keldeo-in-its-cave.jpg\" alt=\"Keldeo in its cave \/ Pok\u00e9mon Unbound\"><figcaption>Keldeo in its cave<\/figcaption><\/figure>\n<table class=\"table grey center\">\n<tbody>\n<td>\n      <strong>Keldeo<\/strong><br \/>\n      Water\/Fighting<br \/>\n      (Lv. 80)\n    <\/td>\n<td><img decoding=\"async\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/missions\/059\/34-pokemon-unbound-keldeo.png\" alt=\"\" style=\"max-width:300px\"><\/td>\n<\/tbody>\n<\/table>\n\n        <a href=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/missions\/\" class=\"parent-page-card\">\n            <picture class=\"card-img\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg\" class=\"attachment-full size-full wp-post-image\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon.jpg 200w, https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-content\/assets\/images\/2024\/07\/missions-icon-150x150.jpg 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\" \/>\t\t\t\t            <\/picture>\n            <span class=\"card-info\">\n                <span class=\"card-info__caption\">Back to:<\/span>\n                <strong class=\"wiki-title\">All Missions<\/strong>\n            <\/span>\n        <\/a>\n\n\t\t\n","protected":false},"featured_media":1355,"parent":282,"menu_order":2,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"_acf_changed":false},"categories":[11],"class_list":["post-1354","wiki","type-wiki","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-missions"],"acf":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/1354","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/wiki"}],"up":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/wiki\/282"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/1355"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=1354"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/unboundwiki.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=1354"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}